metadata.description: We have prepared 6 different artworks that we will use for Proof of Humanity NFT series which will be randomly minted and sent to everyone who donated during the event Web3Go on 24th and 25th of August without any relation to the size of donation. This ticket entitles you to get a Level 2 NFT render of a house with permanent access to information about the construction process, photos of the process, and the final result. Tracking all incoming contributions is possible through a partnership with WhitePay (WhiteBit) and powered by First NFT Agency.
metadata.name: Proof of Humanity
